{"tid":1869761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈咪幫襯奧海城Cinnamxn","createTime":"2020-02-08T10:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T20:55:39.000Z","uid":296170,"like":117,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"c582c45d106330f9ee6d94edd5f6d99b50c2b63f","tid":1869761,"uid":296170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T10:58:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔好再咁戇鳩去奧海城這間Cinnamxn排隊</span> ！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">老闆藍撚到黑！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見到就好撚嬲！！ 事緣這個老闆我朋友識得佢，深藍到黑，<span style=\"color: red;\">成日喺度鬧撚啲抗爭者仆街，扺撚死，殺鳩死晒佢哋</span>！！差人開槍就射得好！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">條友自己拎住外國護照</span>，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢藍扮黃</span></span>！覺得啲人阻鳩哂！將所有FB有關支持藍絲/政府/警察的post全部delete晒！<br />\n<br />\n佢鋪頭琴日開舖，見到咁多人喺度排隊，真係好撚嬲！大家唔好咁戇鳩！益左依啲藍絲扮黃嘅賤人！！你老味！"},{"pid":"5c8fba41642d68182d2d427c7ebbbb7e29d92bbf","tid":1869761,"uid":296170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:39:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab8f359feecf040c14cd080d776a65a080944dc9","tid":1869761,"uid":296170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76740d60b2cea9efaa7b3cbe97bfcd2e27389f8b","tid":1869761,"uid":121080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:31:26.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"9317e737ea74fd99d46e46f66046948bea6235de","tid":1869761,"uid":121080,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:31:52.000Z","msg":"直接去和你eat app report係藍店啦"},{"pid":"69c60182938a188171450acdec67deb6114fe989","tid":1869761,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:32:19.000Z","msg":"幫手推一推！<br